## Governance (ESRS 2 GOV-1 to GOV-5)

### Board Oversight of Sustainability Matters

The Company's Board of Directors exercises oversight of sustainability and
climate-related matters through the {{ board_committee_name | default("Audit and Sustainability Committee") }}.
As of {{ period_end_date }}, the Board comprised {{ metrics.board_size | int }} members,
of whom {{ metrics.board_independent | int }} ({{ "%.0f"|format(metrics.board_independent / metrics.board_size * 100) }}%)
